private theorem left_distrib_aux (n : ℕ) : ∀ a b c : Fin n, a * (b + c) = a * b + a * c :=
  fun ⟨a, ha⟩ ⟨b, hb⟩ ⟨c, hc⟩ =>
  fin.eq_of_veq
    (calc
      «expr ≡ [MOD ]» (a * ((b + c) % n)) (a * (b + c)) n := (Nat.mod_modEq _ _).mul_left _
      «expr ≡ [MOD ]» _ (a * b + a * c) n := by rw [mul_add]
      «expr ≡ [MOD ]» _ (a * b % n + a * c % n) n := (Nat.mod_modEq _ _).symm.add (Nat.mod_modEq _ _).symm
      )
#align left_distrib_aux left_distrib_aux
card:
@[simp]
theorem card (n : ℕ) [Fintype (ZMod n)] : Fintype.card (ZMod n) = n :=
  by
  cases n
  · exact (not_finite (ZMod 0)).elim
  · convert Fintype.card_fin (n + 1)
#align card card
